title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Antonov AN-225 - first release
description:
In this video we will have a look at the Antonov AN-225 which has just been released created by Inibuilds but only available via the MSFS marketplace. Currently only the PC version is available however based on the information available it will become later available on the Xbox due to the WASM functionality which is currently not available on the Xbox.
